      "instruction": "<p>Once the salmon is starting to colour, add your <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong> and the juice<strong> </strong>of your<strong> lemon[s]</strong> (watch out for any pips!) and cook for 3-4 min further on each side or until the salmon is cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
